{
  "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "任意画一个三角形，它身上藏着一个惊人的定理。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "有九个看似毫不相关的点，竟然全都落在同一个圆上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.64,
      "size": 26208,
      "text": "这个圆就叫九点圆，它对每一个三角形都成立。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "mid",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "mid-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/mid-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "先看最简单的三个：三条边各自的中点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "mid",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "mid-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/mid-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.14,
      "size": 34272,
      "text": "它们把三角形的每条边一分为二，是最容易找到的三个点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "foot",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "foot-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/foot-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "再从每个顶点向对边作高，高与对边相交的点叫垂足。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "foot",
      "line_id": "def-4",
      "filename": "foot-def-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/foot-def-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "三条高交于一点,称为垂心,而三个垂足又是三个新点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "ortho",
      "line_id": "def-5",
      "filename": "ortho-def-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/ortho-def-5.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "最后连接垂心与三个顶点，取这三条线段的中点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "ortho",
      "line_id": "def-6",
      "filename": "ortho-def-6.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/ortho-def-6.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "三个中点、三个垂足、三个边中点，一共正好九个点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "奇妙的是,这九个点恰好都在同一个圆上,分毫不差。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "它的圆心是外心与垂心的中点，半径正是外接圆的一半。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-3",
      "filename": "interaction-int-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "切换不同的三角形，你会看到九点圆始终稳稳地穿过它们。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "边中点、高垂足、垂心连线中点，九个点共处一圆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "无论三角形如何变化，这份优雅的秩序都不会改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "这就是几何深处的和谐之美，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 29.0,
  "total_size": 463968
}